  "Description": {
    "English": "The wormhole brain permits the ship <span class=\"name name-technology\">vision of systems far beyond its own experience</span>.  It consists of strands of neural matter, wrapped around a micro-singularity and tethered directly to the ship's visual cortex.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Detailed economic and conflict data</span> will become available on the Galaxy Map, should the ship permit it.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "虫洞脑可以使得飞船<span class=\"name name-technology\">展望远远超出其自身经验的行星系统</span>。 它由多股神经物质组成，包裹着一个微型星体，并直接与飞船的视觉皮层相连。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">如果飞船允许，星系图上可以显示详细的经济和冲突数据</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "蟲洞腦能讓太空船<span class=\"name name-technology\">看到遠超其體驗的星系</span>。擁有神經物質束，包覆在微奇異點上，直接連接到太空船的視覺皮層。<br><br>若太空船允許，可以在銀河系地圖上看到<span class=\"name name-stellar\">詳細的經濟和衝突資料</span>。"
  },
